:menu
cls

echo Please choose an option below to do that function.

if %c%==JAR goto jar

if %c%==colour goto colour

set go=jar2

%java% -cp . *java

set pro2=%pr%jdk1.6.0

set go=jar3

del runserver.bat

del .class

pause
goto menu
set
:colour
cls
echo Would you like to change the backround colour, change
echo the text colour, or reset it to default?
echo.
echo back - Change the backround colour.
echo text - Change the text colour.
echo def - Change all colours back to default.
echo.
echo.
set /p colour=Option:

:text

echo red
echo yellow
echo green
echo blue
echo purple
echo.
echo.

goto menu

set go=r2

goto r3
:r3
if exist .\classes\server.class (goto sl2) else (goto r4)
:r4

%rjava%
pause
cls
goto menu
:r6
set rjava=
set rjava=%java% -cp .;./classes; Server
%rjava%
pause
cls
goto menu
:se
cls
title Error

pause
cls
goto menu
:er
cls

pause
cls
goto menu
:e
cls
exit
:cj
if exist “%pro2%_01%jav%” (goto sj)

goto %go%
